## 1.1
 - Added a new method to the builder: repeat(boolean)
     If true and the player sends an invalid input,
     PlayerChatInputBuilder#onInvalidInput(BiFunction)
     will run and another inputs will be asked.
     If false and the player sends an invalid input,
     PlayerChatInputBuilder#onInvalidInput(BiFunction)
     will run and no more inputs will be expected.
     By default is set to true
